e><br />\n供？"},{"pid":"08868ad3b031a79a893c9f1717fbcd38273b1210","tid":306022,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>09 fit 1.5 朋友放 入唔入手好 低市價 1.5皮左右</blockquote><br />\n姐係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n4皮 3</blockquote><br />\n4皮3上架睇完無問題都買得過嘅"},{"pid":"8cd4f256d23de89d9e2d24ce41e7ab9772729642","tid":306022,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ead31cd77fe728d3c882e4e4574107443315e56","tid":306022,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住村屋唔洗車位好撚爽<br />\n二手mazda3 1.5 2012 車價60,000<br />\n<br />\n牌費一年4000<br />\n保險ncb60 唔洗1000<br />\n油錢$1/km<br />\n部車算新，一年維修約保養2000都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司有免費車位<br />\n<br />\n一個月渣車返工荃灣返九龍灣大概洗1000多d<br />\n，貴過地鐵少少咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗車位真係好抵養"},{"pid":"b0aee8244447a39b082685a6a2058b8388e9ea50","tid":306022,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住村屋唔洗車位好撚爽<br />\n二手mazda3 1.5 2012 車價60,000<br />\n<br />\n牌費一年4000<br />\n保險ncb60 唔洗1000<br />\n油錢$1/km<br />\n部車算新，一年維修約保養2000都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司有免費車位<br />\n<br />\n一個月渣車返工荃灣返九龍灣大概洗1000多d<br />\n，貴過地鐵少少咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗車位真係好抵養</blockquote><br />\n正"},{"pid":"b11eafd2d43e819d7501c0f1c4f30a569744a1ce","tid":306022,"uid":19857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住村屋唔洗車位好撚爽<br />\n二手mazda3 1.5 2012 車價60,000<br />\n<br />\n牌費一年4000<br />\n保險ncb60 唔洗1000<br />\n油錢$1/km<br />\n部車算新，一年維修約保養2000都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司有免費車位<br />\n<br />\n一個月渣車返工荃灣返九龍灣大概洗1000多d<br />\n，貴過地鐵少少咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗車位真係好抵養</blockquote><br />\n正</blockquote><br />\n所以月入萬頭唔會唔夠養車  重點係你想養部咩車同洗唔洗比停車場錢    剩係停車場都夠你入油  even停車場只係千幾蚊一個月"},{"pid":"e68c2c66c1a50fb06cc26d45d350809bd883e7a0","tid":306022,"uid":40179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月入40k想供架c200玩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想供部cla玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d48839f677daf1218cb5610df47f90a277ea65","tid":306022,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>住村屋唔洗車位好撚爽<br />\n二手mazda3 1.5 2012 車價60,000<br />\n<br />\n牌費一年4000<br />\n保險ncb60 唔洗1000<br />\n油錢$1/km<br />\n部車算新，一年維修約保養2000都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司有免費車位<br />\n<br />\n一個月渣車返工荃灣返九龍灣大概洗1000多d<br />\n，貴過地鐵少少咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗車位真係好抵養</blockquote><br />\n正</blockquote><br />\n所以月入萬頭唔會唔夠養車  重點係你想養部咩車同洗唔洗比停車場錢    剩係停車場都夠你入油  even停車場只係千幾蚊一個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我1700車場已經算係輕鬆果班<br />\n假日揸一個月都係2千幾<br />\n如果住村屋，真係一千幾百一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然未計保養"},{"pid":"5908e68976929ac5d4d01bd46a3866f798c026a8","tid":306022,"uid":43520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:11:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔計埋去商場泊車錢？泊街？無試過抄牌？<br />\n唔會揸車去商場？"},{"pid":"a13eccd33852d84707e1c5bb4a564c2b424d9492","tid":306022,"uid":50336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔計埋去商場泊車錢？泊街？無試過抄牌？<br />\n唔會揸車去商場？</blockquote><br />\n去商場都會消費，所以有免泊<br />\n泊得商場嘅車都應該好小會泊街，主要驚人hi花<br />\n正正常常揸應該唔會比人抄牌，冇人叫你雙黃停車，雙白線掉頭同埋超速"},{"pid":"ad250a5ab8dcc66206464426ad42cd9032118710","tid":306022,"uid":66622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"Plan緊買車，不過停車場真係好撚貴，如果夜晚泊街日頭泊番公司唔洗錢有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"62f0b8fda2af3bece97c012e647848993e484e3c","tid":306022,"uid":27080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"養過，賣左<br />\n停車場一年加租一次，頂唔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果停車場要2000樓上，冇20K唔好諗，會養得好煩<br />\n如果唔洗停車場可考慮"},{"pid":"24044bdd00eb841b74dbd56e4fa71f551ec35573","tid":306022,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Plan緊買車，不過停車場真係好撚貴，如果夜晚泊街日頭泊番公司唔洗錢有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n好夜都ok<br />\n今年黑警凌晨都抄"},{"pid":"5bed24719d11357a64ef57f2342a90f0cf332b9a","tid":306022,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Plan緊買車，不過停車場真係好撚貴，如果夜晚泊街日頭泊番公司唔洗錢有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n泊街就預左比人炒既啦<br />\n抄你5,6張可能已經同爛地停車場同價"},{"pid":"e6745fcd1a06c9fd5af0b2915821138506c51198","tid":306022,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Plan緊買車，不過停車場真係好撚貴，如果夜晚泊街日頭泊番公司唔洗錢有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n我樓下夜晚八九點到凌晨一兩點都試過抄，第二朝七點後又抄，晏少少起身隨時中出二連發，我就唔搏啦"},{"pid":"4ac8cc5cf93b600726e0a4f202f9eb7c58f279a0","tid":306022,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"泊番日泊全日泊算喇"},{"pid":"62ddd2340f7bb6b66b9926fe6b2ccdefb0ee6bbb","tid":306022,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"be74240f55a039d40947d0e0306dad91267752e3